snippet.title: Rasternauts
snippet.description:
A pixel perfect way of life is under threat when a scientific experiment gone wrong uncovers a new dimension composed entirely of vectors! Run, jump and shoot your way through over 30 levels to save your bitmapped buddies, hold back the vector invasion, and save all of raster kind!

Coming soon to the Xbox Live Indie Games Channel.
